OL,3,CBBC asks Huw Edwards to give back
OL,4,Csalary earned after November arrest
OL,6,FIt was revealed Edwards was paid an
OL,7,Festimated #200,000 in the period
OL,8,Fbetween his arrest in November on
OL,9,Fthree counts of making indecent images
OL,10,Fof children, and his resignation five
OL,11,Fmonths later.
OL,13,FIt comes after Culture Secretary Lisa
OL,14,FNandy asked the BBC to look into
OL,15,Fwhether it can recoup the earnings.
OL,17,FThere will also be an independent
OL,18,Freview into the organisation's
OL,19,Fworkplace culture, which the Culture
OL,20,FSecretary said she welcomes.
