OL,6,FBefore Edwards resigned from the BBC
OL,7,Fon medical advice in April, he was the
OL,8,Fbroadcaster's highest-paid newsreader,
OL,9,Fwith a pay bracket between #475,000
OL,10,Fand #479,999 for the year 2023/24,
OL,11,Faccording to the BBC's latest annual
OL,12,Freport.
OL,14,FA statement from the corporation said
OL,15,FEdwards had "undermined trust in the
OL,16,FBBC and brought us into disrepute".
OL,18,FIt said: "There is nothing more
OL,19,Fimportant than the public's trust in
OL,20,Fthe BBC; the BBC Board is the
OL,21,Fcustodian of that trust.
