OL,6,F"The Board has met a number of times
OL,7,Fover the last week to review
OL,8,Finformation provided by the Executive
OL,9,Frelating to Huw Edwards. The Board's
OL,10,Ffocus has been principally around two
OL,11,Fissues.
OL,13,F"Firstly, what was known in the lead
OL,14,Fup to Mr Edwards being charged and
OL,15,Fpleading guilty last Wednesday to
OL,16,Fmaking indecent images of children;
OL,17,Fand, secondly, the specifics of the
OL,18,FBBC's handling of the complaints and
OL,19,Fthe BBC's own investigations into Mr
OL,20,FEdwards, prior to his resignation on
OL,21,F22 April 2024".
