OL,6,FThe statement went on to say: "Today,
OL,7,Fthe Board has authorised the Executive
OL,8,Fto seek the return of salary paid to
OL,9,FMr Edwards from the time he was
OL,10,Farrested in November last year.
OL,12,F"Mr Edwards pleaded guilty to an
OL,13,Fappalling crime. Had he been up front
OL,14,Fwhen asked by the BBC about his
OL,15,Farrest, we would never have continued
OL,16,Fto pay him public money. He has
OL,17,Fclearly undermined trust in the BBC
OL,18,Fand brought us into disrepute."
