OL,6,FIt also announced that the Board has
OL,7,Fcommissioned an independent review
OL,8,Fthat will "make recommendations on
OL,9,Fpractical steps that could strengthen
OL,10,Fa workplace culture in line with BBC
OL,11,FValues".
OL,13,FIn response, Culture Secretary Lisa
OL,14,FNandy said that public trust in the
OL,15,FBBC is essential and that she welcomes
OL,16,Fthe organisation's decision to launch
OL,17,Fan independent review into its culture.
