OL,6,FIn a note to staff, he said: "Let me
OL,7,Fbe clear: the villain of this piece is
OL,8,FHuw Edwards; the victims are those
OL,9,Fchildren for whose degradation Huw
OL,10,FEdwards provided a market for."
OL,12,FEdwards admitted three charges of
OL,13,Fmaking indecent photographs of
OL,14,Fchildren after he was sent 377 sexual
OL,15,Fimages - 41 of which were illegal - by
OL,16,Fconvicted paedophile Alex Williams,
OL,17,Fwith seven being of the most serious
OL,18,Ftype.
OL,20,FThe bulk of these, 36, were sent
OL,21,Fduring a two-month period.
